data.meta_description: Windsor Travelmoney - Western Union money transfers, Travelex payment cards and bill payment services in Windsor. Best rates in Windsor. Call 01753 851 005
data.text:
Windsor Travelmoney is located in the heart of Windsor at Windsor & Eton Central train station and open 7 days a week.

We specialise in foreign currency exchange, and will buy back your unused cash when returning from abroad. We have the most common currency always in stock. For larger transactions (Â£500 and above), we offer preferential rates. Please inquire at our office for the most up to date information.

We're open from 9:00 am to 6:00 pm, Monday to Saturday and 10:00 am to 6:00 pm on Sundays.

We can guarantee the best rates for Euros and Dollars in Windsor and charge 0% commission, making us your first stop for travel money.
